      "@id": "urn:toip:glossary:autonomic-identity-system",
      "name": "autonomic-identity-system",
      "description": "an identity system that includes a primary root-of-trust in self-certifying identifiers that are strongly bound at issuance to a cryptographic signing (public, private) key pair. An AIS enables any entity to establish control over an AN in an independent, interoperable, and portable way.",
