      "name": "binding",
      "description": "The technique of connecting two data elements together. In the context of key-event-receipt-infrastructure it's the association of data or an identifier with another identifier or a subject (a person, organization or machine), thereby lifting the privacy of the subject through that connection, i.e. **binding**.",
