      "@id": "urn:toip:glossary:end-verifiability",
      "name": "end-verifiability",
      "description": "a data item or statement may be cryptographically securely attributable to its source (party at the source end) by any recipient verifier (party at the destination end) without reliance on any infrastructure not under the verifier\u2019s ultimate control.",
