      "@id": "urn:toip:glossary:end-verifiable",
      "name": "end-verifiable",
      "description": "When a log is _end verifiable_, it means that the log may be verified by any end user that receives a copy. No trust in intervening infrastructure is needed to verify the log and validate the content.",
