      "@id": "urn:toip:glossary:governance-graph",
      "name": "governance-graph",
      "description": "A graph of the governance relationships between entities with a trust community. A governance graph shows which nodes are the governing bodies and which are the governed parties. In some cases, a governance graph can be traversed by making queries to one or more trust registries.Note: a party can play both roles and also be a participant in multiple governance frameworks.",
