      "@id": "urn:toip:glossary:hourglass-model",
      "name": "hourglass-model",
      "description": "An architectural model for layered systems\u2014and specifically for the protocol layers in a protocol stack\u2014in which a diversity of supporting protocols and services at the lower layers are able to support a great diversity of protocols and applications at the higher layers through the use of a single protocol in the spanning layer in the middle\u2014the \u201cneck\u201d of the hourglass.",
