      "name": "identity-assurance-level",
      "description": "A category that conveys the degree of confidence that a person\u2019s claimed identity is their real identity, for example as defined in NIST SP 800-63-3 in terms of three levels: IAL 1 (Some confidence), IAL 2 (High confidence), IAL 3 (Very high confidence).",
