    {
      "@type": "DefinedTerm",
      "@id": "urn:toip:glossary:proof",
      "name": "proof",
      "description": "A digital object that enables cryptographic verification of either: a) the claims from one or more digital credentials, or b) facts about claims that do not reveal the data \u00a0itself (e.g., proof of the subject being over/under a specific age without revealing a birthdate).",
