      "@id": "urn:toip:glossary:trust-network",
      "name": "trust-network",
      "description": "A network of parties who are connected via trust relationships (such as via a membership agreement) conforming to requirements defined in a legal regulation, trust framework or governance framework. A trust network is more formal than a digital trust ecosystem; the latter may connect parties more loosely via transitive trust relationships and/or across multiple trust networks.",
